Football By Ayaan , Saturday, 11 Feb 2017 
Wayne Rooney has been the pillar of success at Manchester United and his contribution to the club will be remembered for ages to come. Recently, he overtook Bobby Charlton to score the 250th goal of his career, a record for the club. This fan made a video that captures the true journey of the Manchester united kid. Watch it here:
